可能係事業<br />\n可能係因為其他嘢<br />\n世界太多引誘<br />\n現代人連信仰都可以改<br />\n好難講始終如一<br />\n<br />\n我只可以講<br />\n我好鍾意呢一刻嘅自己<br />\n我好鍾意呢一刻深愛你嘅自己<br />\n我好想永遠做呢個自己<br />\n永遠咁等你返嚟<br />\n等唔到就主動去接你<br />\n超級厚面皮咁樣<br />\n永遠黐住你<br />\n我愛你<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知自己打咗乜<br />\n個心好亂<br />\n唉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"take care bro, I know that feel. it fucking sucks."},{"pid":"71b2c31fc5b202d25ad680686647bc92df7361bc","tid":1925284,"uid":48178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"無女朋友無折磨又唔洗擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d99ab2dcb90649571a7e59e6721c42ed0e820f","tid":1925284,"uid":63648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e7833833b0e604e6b25ae4e01db664c53e6d34","tid":1925284,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7bd77fc574ee8926428a24ef0bea415179ce1f6","tid":1925284,"uid":63648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T11:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"我可以儲<br />\n但有錢就唔會變心㗎啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dc9e75e745d404b50c800ae1cf327a86416b4d","tid":1925284,"uid":174717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"798c825f84fb6b1b93b94994b0865e663ed43592","tid":1925284,"uid":192824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"以為樓主想問喊濕左個口罩，係街點換口罩tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0分重作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"仲以為樓豬想問機場邊到有口罩買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}